00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:52.680
It helped us convert a lot of free users to paid users.

00:01:52.740 --> 00:01:54.400
We saw instant success.

00:01:54.820 --> 00:01:58.280
Our daily transactions have grown by 300%.

00:01:58.700 --> 00:02:02.680
We have also seen our number of paying users multiply three times.

00:02:03.220 --> 00:02:08.720
This is very important. Paying users are more engaged and you can monetize them over a lifetime.

00:02:09.220 --> 00:02:13.500
Today six of our top 10 markets in number of transactions

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:13.520
